These layouts have been created from scratch, the XML syntax should be self-explanatory.
Most of the time, 'id' attributes correspond to the XKB name of the key.

All files require utf-8 encoding **WITHOUT BOM**!
Four characters have to be escaped to keep the file XML-compliant:
 "   =>   &quot; (or use single-quote delimiters)
 &   =>   &amp;
 <   =>   &lt;
 >   =>   &gt;

